mixin doc-card(item)
    .doc-card
        .doc-card__icon: i.icm.icm-cross
        .doc-card__surname=item.surname
        .doc-card__name=item.name
        .doc-card__spec Врач ультразвуковой диагностики
        .doc-card__image: img(src=item.image, alt="")
        .doc-card__experience
            span=item.experience
        .doc-card__button
            button.btn.btn--blue.btn--52 Записаться на прием